com.caseybrooks.androidbibletools.enumeration

Enum Book

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Book>
      • com.caseybrooks.androidbibletools.enumeration.BookEnum
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Book>

    public enum Book
extends java.lang.Enum<Book>
    Enumerates all books of Canonical Bible according to their name and the number of chapters in that book. Using the static method parseBook will attempt to find the appropriate enumeration given a string of the book name.
